\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7681550 24. HEALTH}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6970953 
\par 
\par During the past four weeks there have been increasing references to the epidemic of colds and flu, which this week is said to be a widespread topic of discussion (Twelve "Regions, several more th
an once). The epidemic is attributed mainly- to lowered powers of resistance duo to lack of vitamins in the national diet (Six Regions). Other causes mentioned are:
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid7681550 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6970953 (a) The poor quality of leather shoe solos (Four Regions).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7681550 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6970953 (b) War weariness (Two Regions).
