\par The increased amount of drinking, especially among young girls, is}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909220  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6970953 deplored as it is thou
ght to pave the way for V.D. It is again suggested that the "no treating order" should be reintroduced,
