\par (ii)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909220  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6970953 Repair difficulties (Eleven Regions). Reference is made to: The very long time repairs take; The poor quality of leather used for repairs - 'compresse
